MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Remove UHID/Patient ID auto field from registration form (not needed here)
- Add +91 Indian country code prefix with flag to mobile number field
- Style Age as visually distinct auto-calculated read-only field (dashed border, teal bg, lock icon, Auto chip label)
- Improve Date of Birth: calendar icon, teal indicator, max=today, styled picker trigger
- Redesign page header: icon tile + title + breadcrumb + workflow trail with step dots and connectors
- Stepper: pills replaced with connected step dots and step-line connectors
- Form card + action bar now flush connected (no gap, unified rounded corners bottom)
- Sidebar: improved nav item spacing, section captions, active state, user footer
- Full dark mode support maintained via CSS variables throughout
---
